data.name: ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN with(readuncommitted) where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DT, CAS_UNDER_ORD_DEN, COLL_IN_MTH_ACT, CAS_PER_FTE_NUM, CAS_PER_FTE_DEN, CAS_PER_FTE_AVG, CAS_PER_FTE_RNK, COLL_PER_FTE_NUM, COLL_PER_FTE_DEN, COLL_PER_FTE_AVG, COLL_PER_FTE_RNK, CONTRACTOR_NUM from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DT, CAS_UNDER_ORD_DEN, COLL_IN_MTH_ACT, CAS_PER_FTE_NUM, CAS_PER_FTE_DEN, CAS_PER_FTE_AVG, CAS_PER_FTE_RNK, COLL_PER_FTE_NUM, COLL_PER_FTE_DEN, COLL_PER_FTE_AVG, COLL_PER_FTE_RNK, CONTRACTOR_NUM from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = 'JD') order by COLL_PER_FTE_AVG desc

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority3
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DT, CAS_UNDER_ORD_DEN, COLL_IN_MTH_ACT, CAS_PER_FTE_NUM, CAS_PER_FTE_DEN, CAS_PER_FTE_AVG, CAS_PER_FTE_RNK, COLL_PER_FTE_NUM, COLL_PER_FTE_DEN, COLL_PER_FTE_AVG, COLL_PER_FTE_RNK, CONTRACTOR_NUM from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = 'XJ') order by COLL_PER_FTE_AVG desc

data.name: ReadOffice
data.value: select distinct T1.OFFICE_ID, T1.COG_TYPE_CODE, T1.COG_CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.OFF_OFFICE from CKT_OFFICE T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CSE_ORG_RELATN T3 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (T1.COG_TYPE_CODE = T3.COG_PARENT_TYPE) and (T1.COG_CODE = T3.COG_PARENT_CODE) and (T3.REASON_CODE = 'JC') and (@cogChildType = T3.COG_CHILD_TYPE) and (@cogChildCode = T3.COG_CHILD_CODE)

data.name: ReadOfficeStaffing
data.value: select top(1) YEAR_MONTH, F_T_E, OFF_GENERATED_ID from CKT_OFFC_STAFFING with(readuncommitted) where (@offGeneratedId = OFF_GENERATED_ID) and (YEAR_MONTH = @yearMonth)

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 set COLL_PER_FTE_NUM = @collPerFteNum, COLL_PER_FTE_DEN = @collPerFteDen, COLL_PER_FTE_AVG = @collPerFteAvg where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel) and (REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId)

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 set COLL_PER_FTE_RNK = @collPerFteRnk where (REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth) and (REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel) and (REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId)
